text.content: 香港電車及山頂纜車綫路圖
Map of Hong Kong Tramways and the Peak Tram
Western Markets To Shau Kei Wan
Happy Valley To Shau Kei Wan
Shek Tong Tsui To North Point
Shek Tong Tsui To Causeway Bay
堅尼地城至上環（西港城）
Kennedy Town To Shau Kei Wan

注：
1. 電車綫路編號及顔色僅用於區分運行區間，并不表示真實標識色
2. 7號運營區間（堅尼地城至上環）僅在周一至周五繁忙時間運營
3. 本綫路圖上方為西，下方為東

P.S.
1. The numbers and colours are for distinction and are not the real numbers and colours for the transport systems.
2. Line 7 (Kennedy Town to Western Market) is only in service during peak hours in weekdays (Monday to Friday).
3. The upward-facing arrows points to the west in this map.
